{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"641","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"公平貿易組織：女性可可農平均日薪不到0.3美元","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>2020-02-25 00:35 </span><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>經濟日報 編譯陳律安／綜合外電</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>公平貿易組織（<span lang='EN-US'>Fairtrade</span>）表示，女性可可豆農民每日平均收入僅<span lang='EN-US'>23</span>便士（約<span lang='EN-US'>29</span>美分），不僅遠低於極端貧窮線的日薪<span lang='EN-US'>1.4</span>英鎊，也低於一般農民的平均日薪<span lang='EN-US'>75</span>便士，凸顯全球巧克力產業性別薪資差距的問題相當嚴重。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>BBC</span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>報導，公平貿易組織呼籲，英國政府應與巧克力產業一同合作，提高女性薪資。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>公平貿易組織說，英國巧克力產業規模至少<span lang='EN-US'>40</span>億英鎊，且英國人的人均巧克力消耗量，為歐洲最高。因此，公平貿易組織認為，英國應擔任領頭羊，確保所有可可農及巧克力產業員工，尤其是女性，能獲得維持基本生活水準的薪資。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>公平貿易組織呼籲，英國政府與巧克力產業，應加入新的國際倡議組織「可可生活水準收入聯盟」。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/%E5%8F%AF%E5%8F%AF.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 534px;' /></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>公平貿易組織呼籲提高可可農收入。路透</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span lang='EN-US' style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='font-family: &quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif;'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://money.udn.com/money/story/5599/4368407</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-02-26","clk_count":"204"}},"__N_SSG":true}